text: The 2009–10 Welsh National League was the sixty-fifth season of the Welsh National League (Wrexham Area). The Premier Division was won by Rhos Aelwyd, who gained promotion to the Cymru Alliance. ==Premier Division== ===League table=== ==Division One== ===League table=== ==External links== *Welsh National League 2009-10 Premier Division 3
